bedbugs\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ceco is capable of sweeping a standard hotel room in under two minutes, company official Kim Min-su said.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ceco\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"a standard hotel room\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"two minutes\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"company official Kim Min\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"su\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pest control company has teamed up with South Korea's ministries of security and transportation, as well as the Disease Control and Prevention Agency, and is working with airlines and Incheon airport to screen travellers on arrival.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1501, \"end\": 1512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996282934778228, \"rank\": 0.00037184473810772, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\", \"score\": 0.5697108536808656, \"rank\": 0.7552730057988797, \"text\": \"Incheon\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pest control company\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"transportation\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"the Disease Control and Prevention Agency\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"airlines\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"travellers\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"arrival\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, authorities in Par